dataItemLabel.refDataItem: Date Applicants Notified of Qual/Elig Status

dataItemValue.refDataItem: Date Applicants Notified of Qual/Elig Status

dataItemLabel.refDataItem: Date Applicants Notified of Referral Status

dataItemValue.refDataItem: Date Applicants Notified of Referral Status

dataItem.name: Announcement Total Vacancies
dataItem.label: Number of Positions to be Advertised

dataItem.name: Date Announcement Cancelled
dataItem.expression: case when [Vacancy Status]= 'Cancelled' then [Vacancy Last Update Date/Time] else null end

dataItem.name: Interdisciplinary Position
dataItem.expression: case when count (distinct [Vacancy Series]) > 1 then 'Yes' else 'No' end

dataItem.name: Date Applicants Notified of Referral Status
dataItem.expression: minimum(case when [Application Notification Template Type]='Notice of Referral' then [Application Notification Date/Time Sent] end)

dataItem.name: Date Applicants Notified of Qual/Elig Status
dataItem.expression: minimum (case when [Application Eligibility Adjudication]= 'Eligible' then [Application Notification Date/Time Sent] end)

dataItem.name: Certificate Application Notification Template Type
dataItem.expression: [Certificates].[Certificate Application Notifications].[Certificate Application Notification Template Type]

dataItem.name: Certificate Application Notification Date Sent
dataItem.expression: [Certificates].[Certificate Application Notifications].[Certificate Application Notification Date Sent]

dataItem.name: Certificate Review Returned Date
dataItem.label: Date Hiring Decision Rec'd in HR

dataItem.name: Date Final Applicant Statuses Set
dataItem.expression: minimum (case when [Certificate Application Notification Template Type]= 'Notice of Results' then [Certificate Application Notification Date Sent] end)

dataItem.name: New Hire Arrival Verified Complete Date
dataItem.expression: [Certificates].[Certificate Selectee Request Tasks].[New Hire Arrival Verified Complete Date]

dataItem.name: Action Taken
dataItem.expression: case when [New Hire Arrival Verified Complete Date] is not null then 'Hire' else 'Not Filled' end

dataItem.name: Date Applicants Notified of Qual/Elig Status
dataItem.expression: minimum (case when [Application Eligibility Adjudication]= 'Eligible' then [Application Notification Date/Time Sent] end)

dataItem.name: Date Applicants Notified of Referral Status
dataItem.expression: minimum(case when [Application Notification Template Type]='Notice of Referral' then [Application Notification Date/Time Sent] end)
